          <tr><td>Heating element</td><td>$285 – $420</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Heater pressure switch</td><td>$125 – $185</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Door lock / interlock</td><td>$165 – $245</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Door gasket</td><td>$145 – $215</td></tr>
          <tr><td>AutoOpen latch motor</td><td>$165 – $225</td></tr>
          <tr><td>AutoDos dispensing motor (G 7000)</td><td>$245 – $340</td></tr>
          <tr><td>AutoDos PowerDisk dispenser assembly</td><td>$165 – $240</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Turbidity sensor</td><td>$185 – $265</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Flow meter</td><td>$95 – $155</td></tr>
          <tr><td>NTC temperature sensor</td><td>$95 – $145</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Spray arm (upper or lower, single)</td><td>$145 – $215</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Middle rack (3D MultiFlex adjusters)</td><td>$285 – $425</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Salt reservoir / water softener assembly</td><td>$145 – $215</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Main control board</td><td>$580 – $820</td></tr>
          <tr><td>User interface / touch panel</td><td>$385 – $560</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Descaling service (maintenance, no parts)</td><td>$145 flat</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Firmware update via Miele@mobile (no parts)</td><td>$95 flat</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Preventive maintenance visit</td><td>$145 flat</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── WARRANTY ── -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <p class="eyebrow-sub">Warranty context</p>
      <h2>Inside the Miele USA warranty? Call them first.</h2>
      <p>Miele USA dishwasher warranty is 2 years on all parts and labor. During the warranty window, call Miele USA customer service at <strong>1-800-843-7231</strong> for Authorized Service Agent dispatch at no parts cost.</p>
      <p>Post-warranty is where we work. Most of our Miele dishwasher calls are 3-to-12-year-old units where the parts warranty has closed but the appliance has another decade of service life left. Same factory training, faster response, lower labor rate than a post-warranty Authorized Service dispatch. For warranty-overflow situations where Miele USA has a multi-week backlog, we can usually dispatch same-day.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── SERVICE AREAS ── -->
  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow-sub">Where we go</p>
      <h2>Service areas for Miele dishwasher repair</h2>
      <BrandBranchesGrid showHeader={false} />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── RELATED ── -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow-sub">Related Miele services</p>
      <h2>Other Miele categories we service</h2>
      <div class="cat-grid">
        <a href="/brands/miele-refrigerator-repair/" class="cat-card">
          <h3>Miele Appliance Repair</h3>
          <p>Hub page, all Miele categories across Southern California including oven, cooktop, refrigerator, coffee.</p>
          <span class="cat-cta">View hub →</span>
